<body>

    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>From the Principal's Desk</h1>
            <p>A Message to Our Students and Community</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <section class="principal-message">
                
                <div class="principal-photo">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x400.png?text=Principal's+Photo" alt="Photo of the Principal">
                </div>

                <div class="principal-text">
                    <p>
                        Welcome to KASH College, where we are dedicated to providing a comprehensive education to our students in an atmosphere that fosters their development as well-rounded individuals. Our well-qualified faculty strives to sustain quality and academic excellence, encouraging students to participate in various co-curricular and extra-curricular activities, including research, cultural, and sports activities at Colleges, State, and National levels. We have made available necessary infrastructure for the students and organize educational, social, economical, and cultural activities to hone their skills.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        At KASH College, we foster creativity, fortitude, integrity, and leadership qualities among our students for their overall personality development. Our strong commitment to academic excellence, character development, and community service sets us apart from other institutions. We are proud of our alumni who have gone on to make meaningful contributions to society.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We recognize that education is more than just acquiring knowledge; it also involves developing critical thinking skills, empathy, and a sense of responsibility towards the world. We invite students to join us on this journey towards excellence and service, with the aim of creating a better future for themselves and their communities. Come and be a part of the KASH College community and experience our commitment to academic excellence and holistic education.
                    </p>
                    <div class="signature">
                        <h3>Mr. Sudhansu Sekhar Panda</h3>
                        <p class="signature-title">Principal, KASH Campus</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
